org.gvsig.app.gui.preferencespage

Interface PreferenceKeys


  • public interface PreferenceKeys
    The purpose of this interface is to define the keys used for the persistence of this plugin in order to make these keys available on library level, instead of defining them within the preference page (which has UI dependences).
